		<p>We are working on a mini grammar for Skolt Sámi, which is designed especially for users
			of <em><a href="http://oahpa.uit.no/nuorti">Oahpa!-nuõrti</a></em>. </p>

		<p>We have used among other materials: </p>
		<ul>
			<li>Feist, T. 2010: <em>A grammar of Skolt Saami</em>. Manchester.</li>
			<li>Moshnikoff, S. / Moshnikoff J. / Koponen 2009: <em>Koltansaamen koulukielioppi</em>.
				Inari.</li>
			<li>Sammallahti, P. / Mosnikoff, J. 1991: <em>Suomi-koltansaame-sanakirja</em>.
				Utsjoki.</li>
		</ul>

		<p>This is a link to our <a href="http://giellatekno.uit.no/cgi/p-sms.eng.html"> paradigm
